name: Oil-Free Energy Champs
title: Minimal Reliance on Oil for Electricity
description: In 2022, Paraguay produced only 0.002% of its electricity from oil sources, showcasing its commitment to sustainable energy practices.

name: Clean Waste Management
title: Negligible CO2 Emissions from Waste
description: Paraguay's CO2 emissions from waste were a mere 0.0001 Mt CO2e in 2023, highlighting its effective waste management strategies.

name: Regional Export Leader
title: Dominant Exporter to Latin America & the Caribbean
description: In 2023, 66.04% of Paraguay's merchandise exports were directed towards low- and middle-income economies in Latin America & the Caribbean, emphasizing its strong regional trade connections.
